<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. مِنْ النَّصْرِ هَتَّانِ الْجَوَانِبِ وَابِلِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَيَنْبُتُ زَرْعُ الْحَقِّ أَخْرَجَ شطأة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مُسِحًا بِخَيْرٍ لِلثِّمَارِ الْحَوَاصِلِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>إلَهِي فَحَقِّقْ ذَا الرَّجَاءَ فَإِنَّنَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>عَبِيدُكَ تُبْنَا لَسْتَ عَنَّا بِغَافِلِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أغِثْنَا أَغِثْنَا وَأَرْفَعْ الضُّرَّ وَالْبَلا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بِعَفْوِكَ عَنَّا يَا قَرِيبٌ لآمِلِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَإِنْ لَمْ تُغْثِنَا يَا قَرِيبُ فَمَنْ لَنَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لِنَقْصُدَ فِي دَفْعِ الأُمُورِ الثَّقَائِلِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>إِلَيْكَ أَنَبْنَا فَاغْفِرْ الذَّنْبَ وَالْخَطَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إِلَيْكَ رَجَعْنَا فَارْجِعِ الْخَيْرَ كَامِلِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَقَدْ سَامَنَا الأَعْدَاءُ سَوْمًا مُبَرِّحًا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>بِقَتْلٍ وَأَسْرٍ مُوثَقًا بِالْحَبَائِلِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عَلَى غَيْرِ جُرْمٍ غَيْرِ تَوْحِيدِ رَبِّنَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَهَدْمِ قِبَابِ الْمُشْرِكِينَ الأَبَاطِلِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَأَمْرٍ بِمَعْرُوفٍ وَإِنْكَارِ مُنْكَرٍ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَفِعْلِ صَلاةٍ فِي الْجَمَاعَةِ حَافِلِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَأَخْذِ زَكَاةِ الْمَالِ فَرْضًا مُؤَكَّدًا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>يُرَدُّ لِذِي فَقْرٍ وَغُرْمٍ وَعَامِلِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَحَجٍ وَتَقْوِيم الْجِهَادِ لأَنَّهُ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>أَمَانٌ وَعِزٌ عَنْ مَذَلَّةِ خَاذِلِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>